ment of the FIFA Date against Zambia, next Tuesday 31 March from 20.15, at la bombonera\\\" a post from Argentina's official Facebook page read in part.\", \"from\": 4009, \"to\": 4260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4025, \"end\": 4048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3556585747301895e-15, \"text\": \"Argentine national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4057, \"end\": 4071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Scaloni\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lionel Scaloni\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Scaloni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Scaloni\"}, {\"begin\": 4141, \"end\": 4147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.855503199572829e-33, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}, {\"begin\": 4212, \"end\": 4221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999781430235, \"rank\": 2.185611768480037e-08, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Argentina were initially scheduled to play against Guatemala, but the game has been cancelled, forcing the world champions to turn to Chipolopolo.\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4262, \"end\": 4271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999781430235, \"rank\": 2.185611768480037e-08, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4313, \"end\": 4322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.891947292060256, \"rank\": 0.10035760731045114, \"text\": \"Guatemala\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4396, \"end\": 4407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chipolopolo\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be Zambia's second high-profile game against an opponent outside Africa, with their last encounter being against Russia on March 5, 2025.\", \"from\": 4410, \"to\": 4557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4423, \"end\": 4429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.855503199572829e-33, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}, {\"begin\": 4533, \"end\": 4539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8237405458483898, \"rank\": 0.21390980050361208, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Interestingly, Chipolopolo are scheduled to participate in the Four - Nations tournament in Botswana about the same time the Argentina friendly has been scheduled.\", \"from\": 4559, \"to\": 4722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4574, \"end\": 4585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chipolopolo\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4651, \"end\": 4659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999026841, \"rank\": 9.70551038874061e-11, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 4684, \"end\": 4693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999781430235, \"rank\": 2.185611768480037e-08, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Football Association of Zambia (FAZ) is yet to issue a statement.\", \"from\": 4723, \"to\": 4792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4759, \"end\": 4762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.339814980303398e-44, \"text\": \"FAZ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Football_Association_of_Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Mwebantu, Saturday, 21st March, 2026)    Published  on  By  WONDERFUL Group of Companies has launched a marathon, with running enthusiasts expected to turn up on May 30 for the race aimed at promoting the welfare of the girl child.\", \"from\": 4794, \"to\": 5026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The marathon, which will be held under the theme For the Girl Child.\", \"from\": 5028, \"to\": 5096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the Woman.\", \"from\": 5097, \"to\": 5111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For Zambia, was unveiled at an event graced by Minister of Sport, Youth and Arts, Elvis Nkandu.\", \"from\": 5112, \"to\": 5207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5116, \"end\": 5122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.855503199572829e-33, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his speech, Mr. Nkandu described the marathon as a platform for advocacy and inclusion.\", \"from\": 5209, \"to\": 5299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This initiative demonstrates how sport can be used as platform for advocacy and also for inclusion, obviously it can also be looked at as a national development [tool],\\\" Mr Nkandu said, \\\"This Marathon is not merely about physical endurance, it is also about taking collective responsibility, empowerment and shaping the future of our county, about.\\\"\", \"from\": 5301, \"to\": 5651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a speech read on his behalf, Wonderful Group Chief Executive Huang Yaochi said the marathon is aimed at contributing to the health and wellbeing of citizens.\", \"from\": 5653, \"to\": 5813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As we launch the Wonderful Marathon, we do so with confidence that the leadership and associations represented in this room will help guide this platform toward continuity and impact,\\\" Mr. Yaochi said in a speech read by his deputy, Roy Mwamba.\", \"from\": 5815, \"to\": 6060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking earlier, Recheal Tanga, head of the marathon, described the event as the beginning of a movement.\", \"from\": 6062, \"to\": 6168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6088, \"end\": 6093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanga_Region\", \"score\": 0.6736876495303126, \"rank\": 0.4843653166069976, \"text\": \"Tanga\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanga_Region\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanga_Region\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We chose this theme deliberately, to define where we are going and as a decision - that our next chapter must carry greater balance, greater intention and greater responsibility,\\\" Ms. Tanga said.\", \"from\": 6170, \"to\": 6366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6355, \"end\": 6360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanga_Region\", \"score\": 0.6736876495303126, \"rank\": 0.4843653166069976, \"text\": \"Tanga\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanga_Region\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanga_Region\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lusaka Fitness Squad (LFS) President Katai Chola described the marathon as a movement that will celebrate the potential of the Zambian girl child and women.\", \"from\": 6368, \"to\": 6524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6390, \"end\": 6393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nova_Bus_LFS\", \"score\": 0.9999999887531886, \"rank\": 1.1246071138521038e-08, \"text\": \"LFS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nova_Bus_LFS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nova_Bus_LFS\"}, {\"begin\": 6495, \"end\": 6502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.020458240332953e-33, \"text\": \"Zambian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This marathon is a movement that celebrate the strength, resilience, potential for the Zambian girl child\\u2026running has always symbolized progress, every stride forward is a step forward for a brighter future,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 6526, \"to\": 6744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6614, \"end\": 6621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.020458240332953e-33, \"text\": \"Zambian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Others who spoke earlier include Zambia Association of Musicians (ZAM) Brian Bwembya, and Zambia Athletics (ZA) Major Bernard Bwalya, who hailed the initiative.\", \"from\": 6746, \"to\": 6906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6836, \"end\": 6842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.855503199572829e-33, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Mwebantu, Saturday, 14th March, 2026)    Published  on  By  A RUN of poor results has earned Zesco United coach Emmanuel Siwale a suspension while club chief executive officer Kelvin Mutafu has been fired three months into his 2 - year contract.\", \"from\": 6908, \"to\": 7154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6971, \"end\": 6974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RUN_domain\", \"score\": 0.9999940079112449, \"rank\": 5.959933707833478e-06, \"text\": \"RUN\", \"types\": [\"Q8054\", \"Q206229\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RUN_domain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RUN_domain\"}, {\"begin\": 7002, \"end\": 7014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZESCO_United_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zesco United\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZESCO_United_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZESCO_United_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 7021, \"end\": 7029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4430829240774685e-17, \"text\": \"Emmanuel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ZESCO are struggling for form at the moment.\", \"from\": 7156, \"to\": 7200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They sit only three points above the relegation zone having gone the last four matches without a win.\", \"from\": 7201, \"to\": 7302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are 11th with 25 points, three above the relegation zone.\", \"from\": 7303, \"to\": 7365, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The club has responded by sending their coach on suspension.\", \"from\": 7367, \"to\": 7427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The following changes have been made to the technical bench.\", \"from\": 7429, \"to\": 7490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Head Coach Emmanuel Siwale and First Assistant Coach Clive Hachilensa have temporarily been suspended with immediate effect.\", \"from\": 7491, \"to\": 7615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7502, \"end\": 7510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4430829240774685e-17, \"text\": \"Emmanuel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\"}, {\"begin\": 7544, \"end\": 7560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clive_Hachilensa\", \"score\": 0.9999981886010608, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Clive Hachilensa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clive_Hachilensa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clive_Hachilensa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The suspension follows the ongoing review of the team's technical setup and Club performance,\\\" a club statement read in part.\", \"from\": 7616, \"to\": 7741, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the interim, former striker Winston Kalengo will lead the team.\", \"from\": 7743, \"to\": 7809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7774, \"end\": 7789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winston_Kalengo\", \"score\": 0.9999967167149647, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Winston Kalengo\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winston_Kalengo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winston_Kalengo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"During this period, the technical bench will be led by Winston Kalengo, Mwape Mwelwa, Jacob Banda, Emmanuel Mschili and Kondwani Mtonga,\\\" the statement read.\", \"from\": 7811, \"to\": 7969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7867, \"end\": 7882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winston_Kalengo\", \"score\": 0.9999967167149647, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Winston Kalengo\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winston_Kalengo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Winston_Kalengo\"}, {\"begin\": 7898, \"end\": 7909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacob_Banda\", \"score\": 0.9999821909872145, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jacob Banda\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacob_Banda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jacob_Banda\"}, {\"begin\": 7911, \"end\": 7919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4430829240774685e-17, \"text\": \"Emmanuel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\"}, {\"begin\": 7932, \"end\": 7947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kondwani_Mtonga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kondwani Mtonga\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kondwani_Mtonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kondwani_Mtonga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the club also confirmed the departure of CEO Mutafu.\", \"from\": 7971, \"to\": 8034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"ZESCO United Football Club wishes to inform its stakeholders and the public that the Club's Chief Executive Officer, Mr. Kelvin Mutafu has been separated from employment service with the Club with immediate effect.\", \"from\": 8036, \"to\": 8251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8037, \"end\": 8063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZESCO_United_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ZESCO United Football Club\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZESCO_United_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ZESCO_United_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The termination is due to unsuccessful probationally period,\\\" the club stated.\", \"from\": 8252, \"to\": 8330, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(Mwebantu, Saturday, 7th March, 2026)    \\u00a9 Copyright \\u00a9 2026 Mwebantu.\", \"from\": 8332, \"to\": 8401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 8402, \"to\": 8422, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zambia's leading Social news platform.\", \"from\": 8424, \"to\": 8462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8424, \"end\": 8430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.855503199572829e-33, \"text\": \"Zambia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zambia\"}, {\"begin\": 8441, \"end\": 8452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Social_news_website\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Social news\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Social_news_website\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Social_news_website\"}]}]}"